Legendary leader of the Uchiha clan during the Warring States period
Co-founder of Konohagakure (Hidden Leaf Village) with Hashirama Senju
Once a rival and friend of Hashirama, the First Hokage.
Feigned his death and orchestrated events from the shadows
His ultimate goal was to enact the Infinite Tsukuyomi to create "peace."


--Madara Uchiha
